snippet.title: Zedfest - Official Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Zedfest will release on Steam March 16, 2021
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1037080/Zedfest/
Find more info: https://www.zedfestgame.com/

Zedfest is the goriest game show ever created! A hardcore 4 player co-op third-person shooter with the goal to complete objectives while neutralizing Zeds with lots and lots of visceral gore. 

Discord: https://discord.com/invite/tKraWVpkfH


Music: Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio
